song_lyrics: Aum namo namah Aum namo namah Aum namo namah
Aum namo namah Aum namo namah Aum namo namah
Namo namah namo namah he Pramukh Swāmī,
He yug puruṣh sarvottam, he Brahma swayam tīrthottam,
Jug jug jīo tum Pramukh Swāmī,
He yug puruṣh sarvottam, he Brahma swayam tīrthottam,
Parātpar dhar tum Pramukh Swāmī. Namo namah 1
Swāminārāyaṇ Prabhu kī dhārā,
Dharma sanātan gnān hi sārā,
Jan jan ghar ghar tum ne pukārā,
Kalyāṇ path līyā sab sansārā,
He bhavya puruṣh bhaktottam,
He yug puruṣh sarvottam.
He jug jug jīo tum Pramukh Swāmī. Namo namah 2.
Shīl shānti samatā ur mamatā,
Saral amal hṛuday vimal sādhutā,
Jan mangal ek dhyey ramatā,
Ang ang ānand rang jharatā,
He divya puruṣh divyottam,
He yug puruṣh sarvottam,
Ho jug jug jīo tum Pramukh Swāmī. Namo namah 3
Virāg charam par sneh apārā,
Gnān param par naṭ vyavahārā,
Bhakti sabhar tav pal pal sārā,
Sevārat din rāt tumhārā. Namo namah
He puṇya puruṣh parvottam,
He yug puruṣh sarvottam,
Jug jug jīo tum Pramukh Swāmī. Namo namah 4
Anant puṇya prakāsh tumhārā,
Letā agnān andherā hamārā,
Din din patito ko tārā,
Anant puṇya prakāsh tumhārā,
Pūrṇa puruṣh ādarsh hamārā
Bhavya puruṣh ko shat shat vandan,
Puṇya puruṣh ko shat shat vandan,
Divya puruṣh ko shat shat vandan,
Pūrṇa puruṣh ko shat shat vandan,
Yug puruṣh ko shat shat vandan,
Brahma swayam ko shat shat vandan,
Parātpar dhar ko shat shat vandan,
Pramukh Swāmī ko shat shat vandan,
Jug jug jīo Pramukh Swāmī,
Jug jug jīo Pramukh Swāmī...
Namo namah namo namah Pramukh Swāmī,
Namo namah namo namah Pramukh Swāmī,
Namo namah namo namah Pramukh Swāmī...
title: Namo namah namo namah he Pramukh Swāmī
